off]]: Piano Concertos Nos. 1 & 2 \n|[[Boston Symphony Orchestra]] <br>(conducted by [[Seiji Ozawa]])\n|[[Deutsche Grammophon]]\n|459 643-2\n|-\n|2005\n|November 2001\n|[[Bart\u00f3k]]: Piano Concerto No. 1\n|[[Chicago Symphony Orchestra]]<br>(conducted by [[Pierre Boulez]])\n|[[Deutsche Grammophon]]\n|\n|-\n|2006\n|September 2003\n|[[Brahms piano concerto 1|Brahms: Piano Concerto No. 1]]\n|[[Berliner Philharmonic]]<br>(conducted by Sir [[Simon Rattle]])\n|[[Deutsche Grammophon]]\n|\n|-\n|2011\n|February 2009\n|[[Gra\u017cyna Bacewicz|Bacewicz]]: Piano Sonata No. 2; Quintets Nos. 1 & 2\n|Kaja Danczowska (violin)<br>[[Agata Szymczewska]] (violin)<br>Ryszard Groblewski (viola)<br> Rafal Kwiatkowski (cello)\n|[[Deutsche Grammophon]]\n|\n|-\n|2015\n|February 2013\n|[[Lutoslawski]]: Piano Concerto (1987 - 88),Symphony No. 2 ( 1965 -67)\n|[[Berliner Philharmonic]]<br>(conducted by Sir [[Simon Rattle]])\n|[[Deutsche Grammophon]]\n|479 451-8\n|-\n|2017\n|September 2016\n|[[Franz Schubert|Schubert]]: Piano Sonatas D.959 & D.960\n|\n|[[Deutsche Grammophon]]\n|479 7588\n|-\n|2018\n|June 2018\n|[[Leonard Bernstein|Bernstein]]: Symphony No. 2 \"The Age of Anxiety\"\n|[[Berliner Philharmonic]]<br>(conducted by Sir [[Simon Rattle]])\n|[[Deutsche Grammophon]]\n|483 5539\n|-\n|}\n\n===Live albums===\n{|class=\"sortable wikitable toccolours\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:lightyellow; color:black;\"|Date of issue\n! style=\"background:lightyellow; color:black;\"|Date of recording\n! style=\"background:lightyellow; color:black;\"|Cover art\n! style=\"background:lightyellow; color:black;\"|Album details\n! style=\"background:lightyellow; color:black;\"|Collaborating artists\n! style=\"background:lightyellow; color:black;\"|Record label\n! style=\"background:lightyellow; color:black;\"|Catalogue no.\n|-\n|1977\n|\n|\n|[[Piano Sonata No. 8 (Beethoven)|Beethoven: Piano Sonata No. 8, Op. 13 \"Path\u00e9tique\"]]<br>Prokofiev: Piano Sonata No.3, Op.28<br>Bacewicz: Piano Sonata No.2\n|\n|Polskie